# Project Structure

## Technologies
- Bun
- Next.js 15
- React 19
- TypeScript
- Tailwind 4
- Shadcn
- Web3Auth
- Web3
- Wagmi

## Rules

- Prefer types over interfaces
- When building UI, always defautl to Shadcn components

## External APIs
External APIs are integrated in the folder `lib/api/**`.

You may find accompanied API documentation in the folder `docs/*.json` e.g:
- `lib/api/megadata.ts` => `docs/megadata.json`

If an API documentation exists, always refer and adhere to that one when writing the code for using the API, incl. the types.